{"tid":1803756,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社評論：歐洲豪門如皇馬，巴黎明年會簽下中國球員刺激商業收入","createTime":"2019-12-30T12:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T17:30:03.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"49ae69cb1a22205f69c3279cf0343181ceaf1199","tid":1803756,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"路透社來自香港的評論稱，明年豪門俱樂部可能引進中國球員來提高收入。<br />\n 在英國本土版權收入下降的情況下，此舉將提升出售海外版權的收入。<br />\n 報導提到了曼聯這樣的&ldquo;超級豪門&rdquo;，還有武磊這樣留洋的中國球員，稱他在2月的比賽中只花了12分鐘上場時間就吸引了4000萬中國觀眾，和曼聯簽下朴智星後 在韓國取得的銷售增長效果類似。<br />\n 文章還稱，中國球迷大多是&ldquo;人蜜&rdquo;而非&ldquo;隊蜜&rdquo;，所以一次明智的引援會提升海外贊助收入和比賽日收入。 這會刺激俱樂部&ldquo;不顧名聲&rdquo;派上一名水平低於水準的球員上場。<br />\n 文章最後預計，皇馬和巴黎這樣的球隊會在明年簽下中國球員。"},{"pid":"8e75c58e192b64519b7eb693a9359f9f30b95305","tid":1803756,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkbzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=35a6f153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkbzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=6e50a112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要33000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bund